{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"c2b3969afe","title":"中共中央关于海辽轮起义及对船员处理办法给东北局的批复","origin":"根据文件的翻印件打印","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"3001cac3d2","index":0,"year":1949,"month":10,"day":26,"articleId":"c2b3969afe"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-shzygz","name":"中国五十年代初中期的政治运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-shzygz":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"00604ff74f","type":"title","text":"中共中央关于海辽轮起义及对船员处理办法给东北局的批复","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c2b3969afe"},{"id":"30c36bbd36","type":"paragraph","text":"东北局并旅大区党委：","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c2b3969afe"},{"id":"68002e3724","type":"paragraph","text":"号电悉：","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c2b3969afe"},{"id":"33690369c7","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）海辽轮起义及船员给毛主席的信、告国民党海员书与毛主席的复电，新华社迥日皆已发表。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c2b3969afe"},{"id":"760d323a01","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）同意旅大即以党政名义组织欢迎晚会，并可以东北人民政府名义给船员以精神奖励及一定的物质奖励。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c2b3969afe"},{"id":"7c37afffdf","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）船员（特别是技术人员）应尽可能地争取留用，船员走私商品应全部由其自行支配。此外生活上应很好予以照顾。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c2b3969afe"},{"id":"f37cc88d86","type":"paragraph","text":" 中央酉寝","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c2b3969afe"}],"page":{"id":"d08c53741c","publicationId":"CCRD-shzygz","articleId":"c2b3969afe","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}